tools.description:
Query the current status of a claim by claim_id.

Args:
    claim_id (str): The unique identifier of the claim.

Returns:
    dict:
        On success:
            {
                "success": True,
                "data": {
                    "claim_id": str,
                    "status": str
                }
            }
        On failure (claim does not exist):
            {
                "success": False,
                "error": "Claim not found"
            }
Constraints:
    - The provided claim_id must exist in the system.
